	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_LEBENSRAUM_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Anschluss, Irredenta</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_LEBENSRAUM_HELP">
			<Text>The land and peoples of this great City have always belonged to the one true volk. The state must do more to integrate this district more fully into the Empire.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_LEBENSRAUM_HELP_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>The Minefield generates +2 [ICON_PRODUCTION] Production and +10 [ICON_CULTURE] Culture towards border growth.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_LEBENSRAUM_HELP_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>The Courthouse generates +3 [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_LEBENSRAUM_HELP_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>The City enters {5_Turns} of WLTKD, but spends the first 10% of this time in [ICON_RESISTANCE] Resistance.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_LEBENSRAUM_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>The waters surrounding this City are ours by right. We must expand our sea defences outward, to cement our claim.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_LEBENSRAUM_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>War displaced families from their ancestral homes, both in the City and the surrounding countryside. Now that law and a proper respect for the state has been secured, we can begin to invite people back to this City of opportunity!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_LEBENSRAUM_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>While this City is clearly part of our Empire, certain minorities within its precincts deny us. These traitors need to be removed. If they will not swear fealty to the Empire, they shall not be permitted to live in it. Our true people demand it!</Text>
		</Row>
